subject: (anonymous)
body:
I'm thankful for the power of dawn which erases away yesterday's awes and prepares us for new ones. for the chance we're given everyday to start over and for the energy we're delivered to do so though it always hurts.

\- I'm a human being who's trying to adjust to this life without losing much of my identity (7/30/18). [instagram](https://www.instagram.com/lighty_15/).

[what are you thankful for](https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1X6z1T5sSBXxFpfGI7gPZzQIp_qgkDCsVVCLV4yrw1a4/edit)
